Version 1.3.0
----------------

- Create Github-compatible links via the `-g` tag.


Version 1.2.1
----------------

- turn headlines with 7 pounds (`####### headline`) or more into a 
level 6-nested headline since HTML only supports headlines
1-6 (`<h1>, <h2>, ... , <h6>`)



Version 1.2.0
----------------

- support for "closed" atx-style headers, 
  e.g., `### This is an H3 ######`